{"tid":1987291,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"parttime放工之後仲駛唔駛做嘢","createTime":"2020-04-24T11:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T18:20:59.000Z","uid":230225,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e85749d75a5534c983217efc6ea19cca86026550","tid":1987291,"uid":230225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"學生 返緊第一份part time工...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係放工之後啲啊頭仲會係whatsapp group轟炸啲task過嚟 好想知道我係咪收咗工之後都要幫佢做嘢咖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人工已經唔算高 唔想返個pt仔都要賣命<br />\n定係我可以同佢講我下次返工再做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89d04f7de8a244cea78e029b6362cc97e8f7864","tid":1987291,"uid":36383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:25:58.000Z","msg":"no lah, 收工自由時間, part time 係最惡"},{"pid":"f386f39c68136227bf35a45e58605c53e36dd04d","tid":1987291,"uid":36383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:26:13.000Z","msg":"一係計返錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05bc83e12276ed57d1a7c0e8674db98a9571246","tid":1987291,"uid":25573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"覆佢聽日返工處理"},{"pid":"d26b9201c9888eaa990d6e1990ddfd1979441cef","tid":1987291,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:26:46.000Z","msg":"唔駛 <br />\n做就起ot"},{"pid":"62309fa6607affc52e09a0396699a86fc51a6461","tid":1987291,"uid":115700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:26:53.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks就夠<br />\n放工就係放工"},{"pid":"0d5d78833096861c70dc6ff2704cd56eb463e73d","tid